                            </cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>
                                Isabel Allende
                            </cell>
          <cell>
                                The House of the Spirits
                            </cell>
          <cell>
                                1982
                            </cell>
          <cell>
                                magical realism
                            </cell>
          <cell>
                                1942-08-02
                            </cell>
          <cell>
